{"tid":1973623,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"破產手足刑毀罪成 未有申請保釋","createTime":"2020-04-15T09:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T17:34:38.000Z","uid":80162,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"040af7dd608dd7d9257aa6f1ed3cf0eb9b499498","tid":1973623,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:43:40.000Z","msg":"啱先無意中聽到新聞 <br />\n有個手足刑事毀壞黨鐵罪成<br />\n但因為涉事機器價值26萬 <br />\n手足破咗產冇錢賠 <br />\n法官要時間再定刑罰 <br />\n而個手足冇申請保釋 <br />\n依家要繼續還押<br />\n<br />\n屌冇錢問我地拎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人有更多資料"},{"pid":"ed4f862df353032df399b493a5a54b8b641af6f7","tid":1973623,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eed08dd37085fc91b8e37fce8b42eb711256f571","tid":1973623,"uid":80162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"我見啲channel都淨係有侮辱國旗嗰單新聞<br />\n搵唔到呢單刑毀嘅資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52ab42164c48e6d90bd615e006002e01b9c8d54","tid":1973623,"uid":95059,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:50:20.000Z","msg":"手足已成condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e521b49c18c663377f95ebbec3890c1bb698e2","tid":1973623,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"破產男侍應涉破壞逾26萬港鐵設施 辯方指有意認罪 押後答辯研賠償<br />\n<br />\n29 歲男侍應被指去年9 月於港鐵旺角站內破壞閘機及售票機等設施，價值超過26萬，被控一項刑事毀壞罪。案件今日於西九龍裁判法院再提堂，辯方要求押後答辯，透露被告傾向認罪，但由於被告現屬於破產狀態，故辯方需時研究如何賠償。案件獲准押後至5月13日答辯，被告須繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n被告容志強（29 歲，任職侍應）今日沒有保釋申請，還押至今已逾150日。辯方指，據控方文件顯示，遭破壞的設施價值共26萬7千元，由於被告屬於破產狀態，辯方需就被告如何賠償相關款項再作法律研究，故申請押後案件至5月13日答辯，獲裁判官批准。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告於去年9 月 6 日，在旺角港鐵站近 E 出口大堂內無合法辯解下損壞屬於香港鐵路有限公司的 6 部出入閘機、8 部售票機、1 部電視螢幕、1 個八達通機、1 部閉路電視及 1 枝光管，意圖損壞該財產或罔顧該財產是否會被損壞。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A0%B4%E7%94%A2%E7%94%B7%E4%BE%8D%E6%87%89%E6%B6%89%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E9%80%BE26%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E7%AD%94%E8%BE%AF%E7%A0%94%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F/#</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC 3648/2019"},{"pid":"0fea2be834822fc2c73f519d065104e0d31b03de","tid":1973623,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac014e7110cb69ed0e339e5c551156479d7953d3","tid":1973623,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點幫"},{"pid":"a7c7989d1325c3b70d0e654e08011de35611dca3","tid":1973623,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fba87fffd60891d1e98178dca84bc781bd04d36","tid":1973623,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:52:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c68d4efa756d37c764ef71963ac603592dbba7a2","tid":1973623,"uid":314731,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"612呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個幾千萬去左邊到呀？"},{"pid":"8b762f15401408ee851a5872c09efe2c6587a14b","tid":1973623,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"好似之前有人post過上連登<br />\n成班連登仔叫手足申請破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋好似問過612攞錢，612話唔會比錢佢賠"},{"pid":"b873616a03318ac48279b8619f113db546064e84","tid":