 />\n係我捐得比你我寧願你用呢舊錢去幫呢D真係會因為錢而前途盡失既手足<br />\n多過攞舊錢去比中學生買電話同比民陣買音響"},{"pid":"95929412cf2139ab69d4b28204cf82d52b9875b5","tid":1973623,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19a11b4c7cd041d0de77ca09b8af11519ee0907f","tid":1973623,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"73f3c15775d6488cc551f1721b4df19e077564cb","tid":1973623,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:28:57.000Z","msg":"眾籌啦。。"},{"pid":"60f35fb31571ce496a89967f9b4372264fd22333","tid":1973623,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"都破咗產，賠條毛比你"},{"pid":"82dc59a8010428d50d5a7000ee5db0f2f52ed1ca","tid":1973623,"uid":80162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"唔知點解連保釋都唔申請<br />\n照計個律師應該都係義務黃律師<br />\n手足冇錢保釋 個律師都冇理由唔幫佢保釋或者搵支援<br />\n定其實一切都係律師嘅策略嚟 等佢錢都唔洗賠 變社會服務令咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859cc67643e7ae218bd2d9f3d48755dc01d5911b","tid":1973623,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:01:16.000Z","msg":"應該搵邊區區議員幫手?<br />\n定應該搵嗰啲咩咩支援?<br />\n可以點聯絡到佢?<br />\n<br />\n如果賠錢唔洗坐監 26萬真係我地夾比你都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}